'''阿布·雅各布·优素福'''（{{Lang-ar|أبو يعقوب يوسف}}；{{bd|1135年||1184年|10月14日}}），又称'''优素福一世'''<ref name="Mo3jib"/>，[[穆瓦希德王朝|穆瓦希德王朝]][[哈里发|哈里发]]，1163年至1184年在位。

[[塞维利亚|塞维利亚]]的[[吉拉达|吉拉达]]钟楼、[[塞维利亚王宫|塞维利亚王宫]]以及[[瓜代拉堡|瓜代拉堡]]的要塞都是阿布·雅各布·优素福下令修建的<ref name=":23">{{Cite book|last=Bennison|first=Amira K.|title=The Almoravid and Almohad Empires|publisher=Edinburgh University Press|year=2016}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
优素福是穆瓦希德首位哈里发[[阿卜杜勒·慕敏|阿卜杜勒·慕敏]]之子，母亲是[[马斯穆达|马斯穆达]][[柏柏尔人|柏柏尔人]]，外祖父是[[伊本·图马特|伊本·图马特]]的信众之一<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=F3QzDwAAQBAJ|title=Concubines and Courtesans: Women and Slavery in Islamic History|last=Gordon|first=Matthew S.|last2=Hain|first2=Kathryn A.|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=2017|isbn=9780190622183|pages=147|language=en}}</ref><ref name="miranda">{{Cite encyclopedia|year=1986|editor5-last=Heinrichs|editor4-first=E.|editor4-last=van Donzel|editor3-first=C.E.|editor3-last=Bosworth|editor2-first=Th.|editor2-last=Bianquis|editor1-first=P.|editor1-last=Bearman|isbn=9004081143|title=Abū Yaʿḳūb Yūsuf|page=162|volume=I|edition=2nd|publication-place=Leiden, Netherlands|orig-year=1960|first=A.|last=Huici Miranda|url=https://referenceworks.brillonline.com/entries/encyclopaedia-of-islam-2/abu-yakub-yusuf-SIM_0274|publisher=Brill Publishers|encyclopedia=Encyclopaedia of Islam|editor5-first=W.P.|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2019-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213184124/https://referenceworks.brillonline.com/entries/encyclopaedia-of-islam-2/abu-yakub-yusuf-SIM_0274|dead-url=no}}</ref>。优素福在1163年即位。优素福也是一位宗教学者，遵奉[[扎希丽派|扎希丽派]][[伊斯蘭教法學|法学]]，据称会熟练背诵[[布哈里圣训|布哈里圣训]]和[[穆斯林圣训实录|穆斯林圣训实录]]<ref>Shawqi Daif, Introduction to Ibn Mada's ''Refutation of the Grammarians'', pg. 5. Cairo, 1947.</ref>。优素福在宫廷内募集了一批学术名人，哲学家[[伊本·图费勒|伊本·图费勒]]（Ibn Tufail）和[[伊本·鲁世德|伊本·鲁世德]]都曾在其宫廷中任职<ref>Kojiro Nakamura, "Ibn Mada's Criticism of Arab Grammarians." ''Orient'', v. 10, pgs. 89-113. 1974</ref>，通才[[伊本·马达厄|伊本·马达厄]]（Ibn Maḍāʾ）担任其[[首席法官|首席法官]]<ref>{{tsl|en|Kees Versteegh||Kees Versteegh}}, ''The Arabic Linguistic Tradition'', pg. 142. Part of Landmarks in Linguistic Thought series, vol. 3. [[纽约|New York]]: [[劳特里奇|Routledge]], 1997. {{ISBN|9780415157575}}</ref>。优素福在帝国境内推行基于伊本·图马特的宗教改革政策，查禁不符合扎希丽派教义的文献，其子曼苏尔即位后将之集中烧毁<ref>Shawqi Daif, Introduction to Ibn Mada's ''Refutation of the Grammarians'', pg. 6. Cairo, 1947.</ref>。

1170年，优素福进军[[伊比利亚半岛|伊比利亚半岛]]，征服了[[安达卢斯|安达卢斯]]，攻占[[巴伦西亚|巴伦西亚]]和[[加泰罗尼亚|加泰罗尼亚]]，在当地展开掠夺。翌年，他在[[塞维利亚|塞维利亚]]宣告成为安达卢斯的统治者<ref name=pascual424>"The History of the Mohammedan Dynasties in Spain," taken from Ahmed Mohammed al-Maqqari's ''Nafhut Tibb min Ghusn al-Andalus al-Ratib wa Tarikh Lisan ad-Din Ibn al-Khatib''. Translated by Pascual de Gayangos y Arce from copies in the [[大英博物馆|British Museum]]. Pg. 319. [[伦敦|London]]: The Orientalist Translation Fund of [[大不列顛島|Great Britain]] and [[爱尔兰岛|Ireland]]. Sold by W. H. Allen Ltd and M. Duprat.</ref>。

1184年，阿布·雅各布·优素福在围攻葡萄牙[[圣塔伦_(葡萄牙)|圣塔伦]]期间负伤，在返回塞维利亚途中死亡<ref name="miranda2">{{Cite encyclopedia|year=1986|editor5-last=Heinrichs|editor4-first=E.|editor4-last=van Donzel|editor3-first=C.E.|editor3-last=Bosworth|editor2-first=Th.|editor2-last=Bianquis|editor1-first=P.|editor1-last=Bearman|isbn=9004081143|title=Abū Yaʿḳūb Yūsuf|page=161|volume=I|edition=2nd|publication-place=Leiden, Netherlands|orig-year=1960|first=A.|last=Huici Miranda|url=https://referenceworks.brillonline.com/entries/encyclopaedia-of-islam-2/abu-yakub-yusuf-SIM_0274|publisher={{tsl|en|Brill Publishers||Brill Publishers}}|encyclopedia=Encyclopaedia of Islam|editor5-first=W.P.|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2019-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213184124/https://referenceworks.brillonline.com/entries/encyclopaedia-of-islam-2/abu-yakub-yusuf-SIM_0274|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其遗体葬于丁梅尔<ref name="Mo3jib">Abdelwahid al-Marrakushi "al-Mojib fi Talkhis Akhbar al-Maghrib" [The Pleasant Book in Summarizing the History of the Maghreb] (1224) pp.125-126</ref>。

